-= Kitchen =-
You're now in a kitchen.

You see a fridge. Empty! What kind of nightmare TextWorld is this? You scan the room for an oven, and you find an oven. Now that's what I call TextWorld! You can see a table. The table is massive. You bend down to tie your shoe. When you stand up, you notice a counter. Why don't you take a picture of it, it'll last longer! You see a red hot pepper on the counter. Look over there! a stove. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. You swear loudly.

There is an open screen door leading north. There is a closed frosted-glass door leading south. There is an exit to the west.
